---
import LegalPage from '@/components/legal/LegalPage.astro';
---

<LegalPage
  title="Privacy Policy | Black Knight Roofing"
  description="Learn how Black Knight Roofing collects, uses, and protects information submitted through this website."
  heading="Privacy Policy"
  intro="This policy explains what information we collect through the Black Knight Roofing website, how we use it, and how to contact us about privacy-related questions."
>
  <p>
    Black Knight Roofing uses this website to share information about our company and services and to respond to
    homeowner and property-owner inquiries. By using this website or submitting a form, you acknowledge the practices
    described in this Privacy Policy.
  </p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We collect information you choose to provide when you contact us through this website, including:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Name</li>
    <li>Phone number</li>
    <li>Email address</li>
    <li>Property ZIP code or project location details</li>
    <li>Requested service type</li>
    <li>Project notes, questions, or other information you include in a message</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    We may also receive limited technical or security-related information generated by website infrastructure, such as
    browser, device, or network details used to keep the site available and reduce spam or abuse.
  </p>

  <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
  <p>We use submitted information to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Respond to quote requests, inspection requests, and general inquiries</li>
    <li>Contact you about the roofing, exterior, or related project you asked us about</li>
    <li>Schedule consultations, inspections, or follow-up conversations</li>
    <li>Improve how we handle incoming leads and customer-service requests</li>
    <li>Maintain website security and reduce fraudulent or abusive submissions</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    We do not describe your submission as confidential or legally privileged, and you should avoid sending sensitive
    personal information that is not necessary for us to respond to your request.
  </p>

  <h2>Google reCAPTCHA and Security Services</h2>
  <p>
    This site references Google reCAPTCHA to help protect forms and reduce spam or automated abuse. Use of reCAPTCHA
    is subject to the
    <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Privacy Policy</a>
    and
    <a href="https://policies.google.com/terms" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Terms of Service</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>How Long We Keep Information</h2>
  <p>
    We retain submitted contact information for as long as reasonably necessary to respond to your request, manage
    customer communications, maintain business records, and address legal, operational, or warranty-related matters.
  </p>

  <h2>How We Share Information</h2>
  <p>
    We may share information with service providers or partners who support website hosting, communication, operations,
    or lead handling on our behalf. We may also disclose information when reasonably necessary to comply with law,
    protect rights, investigate abuse, or enforce our website terms.
  </p>

  <h2>Your Choices</h2>
  <p>
    You can choose not to submit website forms, but that may limit our ability to respond or schedule service. If you
    want us to review, update, or delete information you previously submitted, contact us using the details below and
    describe your request.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact Us About Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    For privacy questions or requests, contact Black Knight Roofing at
    <a href="mailto:support@blackknightroofing.com">support@blackknightroofing.com</a>
    or
    <a href="tel:7208059666">(720) 805-9666</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>Related Pages</h2>
  <p>
    You can also review our <a href="/terms-of-use">Terms of Use</a>, <a href="/accessibility">Accessibility</a>, and
    <a href="/company-info">Company Info</a> pages.
  </p>
</LegalPage>
